reviewText: Love this movie!!  Kim Woo Bin is awesome!!
I saw this on Drama Fever and anything with Kim Woo Bin I love.
This is a great movie!!  I love Lee Hyun Woo and he does not disappoint in this movie. It is filled with intrigue and the ending twist is great!  I totally recommend it!!!!

Really cool movie! I had seen it online but I only purchase it on DVD if I really liked it. This one was one of the best heist movies I've seen yet. The acting was great, the plot was good, and the movie it didn't lag. Plus the awesome twist at the end left me speechless! Overall great movie I wanted to show it to all my friends.
This is a great film.  The characters are well cast and the plot has you on the edge of your seat.  I recommend to anyone!
